Package frc.qefrc.qelib.drive

Class QEDiffDrive

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.qefrc.qelib.drive.QEDiffDrive
  • public class QEDiffDrive
extends Object
    NOT DONE DO NOT USE

    Fancier Differential Drive handler class that is designed for use with 4 REV Robotics NEO/Spark Max pairs (2 Per Side) attached to a single-speed gearbox. Current defaults are based on a 2023 Kit of Parts chassis.
